On top of DOCUMENT_ROOT not set, there is also a 2nd value that would not be set for this to occur: 
```php
$config = (array)Configure::read('App') + [
            'base' => null,
            'webroot' => null,
            'baseUrl' => null,
        ];
$baseUrl = $config['baseUrl'];
...
$base = dirname($baseUrl);
```
in

```php
        $docRoot = $server['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] ?? null;
        if (
            (!empty($base) || !str_contains($docRoot, $webroot))
            && !str_contains($webrootDir, '/' . $webroot . '/')
        ) {
            $webrootDir .= $webroot . '/';
        }
```
